<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:08:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国对以色列在加沙的失望已经转化为愤怒。哈马斯最先注意到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/as-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-escalates-u-s-patience-with-israel-is-running-out/0000018e-0ae5-d3bd-afce-bbe795eb0000</link><description>这一变化主要是由美国副总统呼吁立即停火发出的，哈马斯已经注意到了这一变化，哈马斯似乎在谈判中采取了更强硬的立场。除了内塔尼亚胡寻求政治生存之外，华盛顿正在努力确定以色列的战争战略</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/as-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-escalates-u-s-patience-with-israel-is-running-out/0000018e-0ae5-d3bd-afce-bbe795eb0000</guid></item><item><title>几位利库德集团部长反对斯莫特里奇绕过法院裁决为犹太学院提供资金的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/several-likud-ministers-oppose-smotrichs-plan-to-bypass-court-ruling-to-fund-yeshivas/0000018e-0ae7-d857-adff-cfff11e60000</link><description>据以色列总检察长称，如果新的法律草案在 3 月底前未获得通过，犹太学院基金将被暂停。无论如何，FM Smotrich 为犹太学院提供资金的想法引起了利库德集团部长们的愤怒，他们认为这会因对正统征兵豁免的愤怒而引起公众的愤怒</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/several-likud-ministers-oppose-smotrichs-plan-to-bypass-court-ruling-to-fund-yeshivas/0000018e-0ae7-d857-adff-cfff11e60000</guid></item><item><title>遭到以色列抵制的开罗会谈没有取得突破；美国要求拉法制定人道主义计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-live/u-s-vp-harris-urges-humanitarian-plan-before-any-rafah-action-in-meeting-with-gantz/0000018e-0c97-d5ee-a78e-3cd7db650000</link><description>甘茨表示，他在美国会谈期间“强调了在加沙建立国际政府的重要性” ■ 以色列国防军称汗尤尼斯的战斗仍在继续 ■ 加沙最大的隧道被发现被毁 ■ 哈马斯报告称，过去一天有 97 人死亡 ■ 联合国报告发现“性暴力的明确证据” 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中的以色列受害者、人质 ■ 印度国民在以色列北部被反坦克导弹杀死，七人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article-live/u-s-vp-harris-urges-humanitarian-plan-before-any-rafah-action-in-meeting-with-gantz/0000018e-0c97-d5ee-a78e-3cd7db650000</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告发现哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击、人质事件中以色列受害者的“性暴力和强奸的明确证据”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/un-report-clear-evidence-of-sexual-violence-rape-during-and-after-hamas-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0b47-d3bd-afce-bbc7a2ac0000</link><description>以色列欢迎“最终承认”哈马斯的性犯罪，但拒绝调查巴勒斯坦有关以色列人性暴力的指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 22:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/un-report-clear-evidence-of-sexual-violence-rape-during-and-after-hamas-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0b47-d3bd-afce-bbc7a2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>当甘茨和加兰特挑战内塔尼亚胡时，掌握总理权力的不仅仅是极右派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/as-gantz-gallant-defy-netanyahu-its-not-just-the-far-right-that-hold-power-over-the-pm/0000018e-0b13-d9cb-afdf-0b9fe0070000</link><description>甘茨对白宫的流氓访问和加兰特对法案草案的强硬否决，为内阁成员针对内塔尼亚胡的叛变翻开了新的篇章。由于紧急“团结”政府，总理的极右翼盟友并不是唯一能够瓦解联盟的人</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/as-gantz-gallant-defy-netanyahu-its-not-just-the-far-right-that-hold-power-over-the-pm/0000018e-0b13-d9cb-afdf-0b9fe0070000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡要求将腐败审判的证词推迟到战后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-to-postpone-testimonies-in-corruption-trial-until-after-war/0000018e-0aa7-d5ee-a78e-3ae716790000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的律师向法庭提出动议，要求“只要国家安全局势没有实质性变化”就推迟作证，理由是加沙战争导致总理与其法律团队之间沟通困难。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-to-postpone-testimonies-in-corruption-trial-until-after-war/0000018e-0aa7-d5ee-a78e-3ae716790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家委员会关于梅龙山灾难的报告将于本周发布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-report-on-mount-meron-disaster-to-be-released-this-week/0000018e-0ac9-d857-adff-cff946cf0000</link><description>2021 年 4 月，以色列北部梅龙山的 Lag B&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动期间发生人群拥挤事件，造成 45 人死亡。调查委员会询问了包括总理内塔尼亚胡和警察局长在内的证人，并警告说“他们可能会受到该报告的影响”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:39:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-report-on-mount-meron-disaster-to-be-released-this-week/0000018e-0ac9-d857-adff-cff946cf0000</guid></item><item><title>抵达以色列机场的乘客报告称，由于司机对新的 Gett 政策做出反应，出租车等待时间为两小时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/passengers-arriving-in-israel-report-two-hour-wait-for-cabs-as-gett-changes-pick-up-policy/0000018e-0a7e-d5ee-a78e-3afebb2b0000</link><description>Gett 是一家实际上垄断了以色列出租车市场的叫车公司，它改变了在本古里安机场的接机政策，要求乘客通过他们的应用程序或在信息亭订购出租车，而不是使用现金</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:24:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/passengers-arriving-in-israel-report-two-hour-wait-for-cabs-as-gett-changes-pick-up-policy/0000018e-0a7e-d5ee-a78e-3afebb2b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府如何处理“以色列问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-the-biden-administration-is-dealing-with-its-israel-problem/0000018e-0a76-d3bd-afce-bbf756d10000</link><description>本周很可能成为以色列加沙战争以及拜登政府立场的转折点，在斋月前几天，许多路径会汇合</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:14:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-the-biden-administration-is-dealing-with-its-israel-problem/0000018e-0a76-d3bd-afce-bbf756d10000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 150 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-150/0000018e-0aa8-d5ee-a78e-3aea95110000</link><description>30 岁泰国工人被从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射的反坦克导弹炸死 ■ 拜登表示，他希望看到以色列大幅减少在加沙的武力 ■ 近东救济工程处将发布报告，指责以色列虐待自此以来一直被拘留的加沙人战争开始 ■ 贝鲁特的哈马斯官员呼吁中东各地的巴勒斯坦人将斋月期间的每一天都变成“冲突的一天” ■ 这是战争爆发 150 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-150/0000018e-0aa8-d5ee-a78e-3aea95110000</guid></item><item><title>反坦克导弹袭击黎巴嫩边境附近的以色列农场，造成一名外国工人死亡、七人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/one-foreign-worker-killed-seven-wounded-in-anti-tank-missile-strike-in-northern-israel/0000018e-0a32-d5ee-a78e-3af2a5860000</link><description>死者是印度公民，在以色列北部与黎巴嫩接壤的莫沙夫·马加利奥特社区工作时被杀。这些工人最近抵达以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/one-foreign-worker-killed-seven-wounded-in-anti-tank-missile-strike-in-northern-israel/0000018e-0a32-d5ee-a78e-3af2a5860000</guid></item><item><title>拜登开始支持抵抗内塔尼亚胡及其战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/biden-is-now-arming-the-resistance-to-netanyahu-and-his-war/0000018e-09a4-d822-a9ce-7db708370000</link><description>美国犯了一个代价高昂的错误：对内塔尼亚胡的无条件支持助长了加沙的屠杀。但现在，姗姗来迟的巨变正在发生</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/biden-is-now-arming-the-resistance-to-netanyahu-and-his-war/0000018e-09a4-d822-a9ce-7db708370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士：“激怒”内塔尼亚胡试图破坏甘茨的美国之行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-enraged-netanyahu-trying-to-undermine-gantz-u-s-visit/0000018e-08a9-d822-a9ce-7dbfdcbb0000</link><description>由于以色列总理和拜登总统之间的关系日益紧张，内塔尼亚胡对战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨邀请访问华盛顿感到愤怒，决心“向美国政府发出信号，表明它与错误的本杰明会面”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-enraged-netanyahu-trying-to-undermine-gantz-u-s-visit/0000018e-08a9-d822-a9ce-7dbfdcbb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的民主尚未得救：司法政变最终如何获胜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-democracy-hasnt-been-saved-how-the-judicial-coup-eventually-prevailed/0000018d-fa9e-d1c2-af9f-ffbfe72b0000</link><description>司法部长亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 公布削弱司法机构的计划 14 个月后，尽管高等法院的一项裁决拯救了合理性标准，但该标准已被削弱，法院现在拥有保守派多数</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-democracy-hasnt-been-saved-how-the-judicial-coup-eventually-prevailed/0000018d-fa9e-d1c2-af9f-ffbfe72b0000</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，非利士人崇拜希腊母神，在邪教中使用毒品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/philistines-worshipped-greek-mother-goddess-used-drugs-in-cult-study-shows/0000018e-09d6-d5ee-a78e-39d60d5b0000</link><description>对圣经巨人歌利亚的出生地迦特神庙中植物遗骸的分析表明，非利士宗教包括外国和当地迦南仪式的混合体</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/philistines-worshipped-greek-mother-goddess-used-drugs-in-cult-study-shows/0000018e-09d6-d5ee-a78e-39d60d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的残酷性被其权力下放所掩盖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-cruelty-is-concealed-by-its-decentralization/0000018e-0970-d857-adff-cff9519e0000</link><description>就像一种看不见的化学元素一样，以色列的残暴行为已经在时间和空间中蔓延，由于其同谋者数不胜数且大多匿名，因此以色列的残暴行为一直处于隐蔽状态。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-cruelty-is-concealed-by-its-decentralization/0000018e-0970-d857-adff-cff9519e0000</guid></item><item><title>WZO 的自由派集团声称在年度会议上战胜了极端分子和福音派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/wzos-liberal-bloc-claims-victory-over-extremists-and-evangelicals-at-annual-confab/0000018e-0984-d3bd-afce-b9c7952e0000</link><description>世界犹太复国主义组织代表通过决议，使奥兹玛·耶胡迪特等极右团体难以竞选世界犹太复国主义大会，也使那些属于其他宗教的人难以以“自我认同的犹太人”身份投票</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/wzos-liberal-bloc-claims-victory-over-extremists-and-evangelicals-at-annual-confab/0000018e-0984-d3bd-afce-b9c7952e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家庭在议会举行无声游行，并附上被俘亲人的照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-families-hold-silent-march-at-knesset-with-photos-of-captive-loved-ones/0000018e-0955-d5ee-a78e-39d7e98c0000</link><description>在以色列议会关于人质家庭健康问题的会议上，与会者猛烈抨击了以色列政府对人质危机的处理方式，其中一位与会者表示，“日子一天天过去，什么也没有发生”，并补充道，“这些家庭都快被淹死了”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-families-hold-silent-march-at-knesset-with-photos-of-captive-loved-ones/0000018e-0955-d5ee-a78e-39d7e98c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列对约旦河西岸首都拉马拉进行了多年来最大规模的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/israel-carries-out-largest-raid-in-west-bank-capital-ramallah-in-years-palestinians-say/0000018e-08e9-dbc9-a38f-b8fb3c2d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报告称，加沙战争期间西岸暴力事件激增，以色列军队在连夜突袭中杀死了一名 16 岁男孩</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/israel-carries-out-largest-raid-in-west-bank-capital-ramallah-in-years-palestinians-say/0000018e-08e9-dbc9-a38f-b8fb3c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，被绑架以色列士兵的父亲发现了令人不安的细节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/kidnapped-israeli-soldiers-father-discovers-disturbing-details-on-october-7/0000018e-04f2-d3bd-afce-b5f3c50d0000</link><description>一辆装备精良、防护严密的坦克是如何在10月7日一早落入哈马斯手中，导致以色列士兵被杀和绑架的？</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/kidnapped-israeli-soldiers-father-discovers-disturbing-details-on-october-7/0000018e-04f2-d3bd-afce-b5f3c50d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>